# Tailwind CSS Guidelines

## Tailwind CSS Guidelines
- Use utility-first approach
- Create custom components for reusable UI elements
- Use Tailwind's responsive design utilities
- Implement dark/light mode support
- Use [Nuxt ChadCN](https://nuxt.com/modules/shadcn) ([Docs](https://www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/installation/nuxt))
- Use semantic color names and consistent spacing
- Optimize for mobile-first responsive design